{"tid":130131,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果食野貨不對版，你地會點？","createTime":"2017-02-22T07:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T11:21:23.000Z","uid":1167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ae238216b01e90169bdf6ae92e6219b98f611d3","tid":130131,"uid":1167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T07:11:50.000Z","msg":"話說琴日同條女去食野<br />\n叫左個飯，話送上湯時菜<br />\n點知黎左個紫菜碎蛋碎湯（全部係碎）<br />\n擺明搵鳩笨柒啦<br />\n我條女話係呀，有湯有紫菜，無問題<br />\n我搵個疑似經理既問<br />\n佢話：係咁架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另一個仲怒啤我，問我想點<br />\n條女仲係咁幫手話無問題呀，生意難做<br />\n我真係唔介意食少碟菜<br />\n但間野真係態度惡劣，呃鳩人<br />\n最撚嬲係條女真係on99<br />\n<br />\n有圖有真相<br />\n碗湯無飲過<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2D81oN3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2D81oN3.jpg&h=a40dc82c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yK8Kx6C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyK8Kx6C.jpg&h=b328b1be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D3qcW5S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD3qcW5S.jpg&h=25069cf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁撚樣食一食都137蚊，又唔好食又搵笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d6c949e734e47d242dbd5097d1e196a7133e65","tid":130131,"uid":1167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T07:13:27.000Z","msg":"唔想大家中伏，推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4608286da3d4c229435f371edb8eaa7c0f976ed5","tid":130131,"uid":1167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T07:21:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921db9663d6b307451c56cb88d7bda72b0546f07","tid":130131,"uid":1167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T08:00:27.000Z","msg":"認真野無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e9165694e72898b1b0b334e4e0b769e2ea326e","tid":130131,"uid":7943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T08:03:13.000Z","msg":"影下野食喇 <br />\n間間茶記啲湯都係hea"},{"pid":"a3513cd7044df6500bcbfe024ccfbda2e763f23a","tid":130131,"uid":5250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T08:05:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"671af54d6323fe92a8d6def96b0c9cd0c2fc3321","tid":130131,"uid":30395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T08:14:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b2d3df8da18444d87d5b192b3b6839aaba84329","tid":130131,"uid":1167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T09:00:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>影下野食喇 <br />\n間間茶記啲湯都係hea</blockquote><br />\n問題唔係湯，係佢話送時菜<br />\n但最黎黎左碗唔知乜當係"},{"pid":"43c4872e12572132e6e9f86c6c413847f6173f35","tid":130131,"uid":1167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T09:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8b9f009dfdb534bd826397299db2d8742852fd","tid":130131,"uid":1167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T11:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}